I"i<p>This is one of our passion projects. If a stock price series is
mean-reverting, we can trade on it and make a profit if we can accurately
estimate its mean and the standard deviation for the near future. Kalman filter is
an excellent technique for doing that. Read our <a href="/assets/stock-price-forecasting-with-kalman-filter.pdf">paper</a> to learn how Kalman filter works its magic.</p>

